query:
SELECT ul.id, ul.tenantId, ul.userId, ul.isActive, u.name, u.email, u.superAdmin 
FROM userLicenses ul 
LEFT JOIN users u ON ul.userId = u.id 
WHERE ul.tenantId = 1;
